
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Edit Player</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Slab:wght@200&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
  <div class="navbar">
    <h3><a href="/">Home</a></h3>
    <h3><a href="/players">My Team</a></h3>
  </div>

  <p>views/players/show</p>
  <div class="body-players-show">
    <div class="edit-link">
      <h2><a href="/players/<%=players._id%>/edit">Edit this player</a></h2>
    </div>
  
    <div class="player-info">
      <div class="player-description">
        <h4><%= players.name %> is a captivating and dazzling magician on the field, with an unrivaled mastery of the <%= players.foot %> foot.</h4>
        <p>Sporting an awe-inspiring rating of <%= players.rating %>,</p>
        <p>this player effortlessly weaves through opponents like a nimble gazelle. Adorned with the prestigious number <%= players.number %>,</p>
        <p>they bring an unmatched level of finesse, power, and grace to the game. As a <%= players.position %>, they strategically orchestrate</p>
        <p>the flow of the match, conducting the team with impeccable vision and precision. With every touch of the ball, they create pure magic,</p>
        <p>leaving both fans and rivals spellbound. From audacious dribbles to jaw-dropping goals, <%= players.name %> is a true maestro of the pitch.</p>
        <p>Their unrivaled skills and cunning tricks make even the most skilled defenders tremble in fear.</p>
        <p>Prepare to be mesmerized by the sheer artistry and flair that <%= players.name %> brings to the beautiful game.</p>
        <p>Whether it's a flick, a pass, or a thunderous strike, they always find a way to leave a lasting impression.</p>
        <p>So sit back, relax, and witness the footballing brilliance of <%= players.name %> in action - an experience you won't soon forget!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  

  
  

  


</body>
</html>


